dct_description_sm: Shows cities and towns (represented by a variety of symbols), waterways, islands.
3 bar scales in "Stades Olympiques," "Milles Romains," and "Stades d'Alexandre."
Likely from: Histoire des hommes ... Explication des gravures. Cahier pour l'abonnement de 1782; in vol. 12 of "Histoire des hommes. Partie de l'histoire ancienne" of Delisle de Sales.
